MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 364c2b772391e46dba637935c558b9b2, type: 3}
  m_Name: Elf
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::MythSO
  pageNumber: 69
  mythName: Elf
  omens:
  - '1. Along a sheltered stream, isolated signs of

    the next Season arriving
    early.'
  - '2. Two season destroyers are about to kill a

    defenceless, defeated ironsmith
    outside

    his tiny forge. They claim the tide of

    seasons requires fresh
    blood.'
  - '3. A season scout carries the rod of the

    upcoming Season, wishing to gift
    it to a

    Seer courtesy of the Elf. The rod holds the

    power to usher
    in its Season early.'
  - '4. A season scout gifts the bow of the

    upcoming Season (d8 long) to the
    Knight

    with the highest SPI score. It is imbued

    with the power of the
    upcoming Season,

    when it is more potent (2d8).'
  - '5. A season scout is travelling to the Seat of

    Power to deliver a message
    to the ruler of

    the Realm. They carry the longly viper, a

    leaping,
    talking snake. Only the viper

    knows the message, that the Elf is coming

    to
    claim this Realm as their own.'
  - '6. The Elf emerges to claim the Seat of

    Power, a Warband each of scouts
    and

    destroyers. They''d prefer a duel.'
  verse: 'A steward of seasons, nature'' s power bestowed

    Our land bends to
    their whimsy, our lives no mercy showed'
  castEntries:
  - name: The Elf, Steward of Seasons, Coredis
    statBlock: 'VIG 9, CLA 9, SPI 9, 13 GD

      Acts first, faster than any opponent.'
    notes: 'Wants to flaunt their power.

      In Spring: SPI 19 and swiftbow (2d6
      long)

      In Harvest: VIG 19 and goldfalx (3d6 long)

      In Winter: CLA
      19 and claws and jaws (4d6)'
  - name: Season Scouts, Tizra, Vioth, Santrosal
    statBlock: 'VIG 8, CLA 16, SPI 12, 8 GD

      Swiftbow (2d6), strawlike hair,
      zero patience'
    notes: Flee when wounded, faster than any mortal.
  - name: Season Destroyers, Kilunar, Tasiviza
    statBlock: 'VIG 10, CLA 12, SPI 12, 8 GD

      A2 (smoothbark armour, helm)'
    notes: Goldfalx (3d6 long), sense of superiority
  flavorTable:
    title: QUIRKS OF THE ELF AND THEIR KIN
    columns:
    - header: Cannot
      values:
      - Harm animals
      - Harm plants
      - Feel emotion
      - Speak
      - Step indoors
      - Tolerate music
    - header: Absolutely Must
      values:
      - Extinguish fires
      - Kill the elderly
      - Scare children
      - Steal jewellery
      - Consume food seen
      - Punish the ugly
  visibleByDefault: 0
  visibleMarkerPrefab: {fileID: 0}
